org.mcm.sws.xmlschema
Class XSSchema

java.lang.Object
  org.mcm.sws.xmlschema.XSNode
      org.mcm.sws.xmlschema.XSSchema
public class XSSchema
extends XSNode

This XML schema implementation is used for correclty instantiating outgoing XML messages. This does NOT require very fine grained validity checks; therefore, this implementation does NOT provide the means to correctly validate XML documents.

Author:
Joachim Peer
